# Local privacy mode

This project uses **local inference only**. All prompts and code context must stay on-device.

## Rules

- Do not suggest sending code, credentials, or internal documents to cloud APIs.
- Prefer the configured local model via oMLX (`http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1`).
- When reviewing security-sensitive changes, remind the user that Cursor Tab autocomplete is still cloud-hosted.

## Stack reference

- Hub: http://127.0.0.1:3080/hub
- Chat: http://127.0.0.1:3080
- Document RAG: Open WebUI Knowledge Collections (Work / Personal)
